## ðŸ“‹ **Quality Assurance**

### **Pre-Sync Validation**

- [ ] **Content consistency** between source and target files
- [ ] **Navigation templates** match file location and context
- [ ] **Relative paths** calculated correctly for file structure
- [ ] **No duplicate navigation** elements in files

### **Post-Sync Validation**

- [ ] **All related files** updated consistently
- [ ] **Navigation links** work correctly
- [ ] **No broken references** or 404 errors
- [ ] **Styling consistency** across all pages
- [ ] **Test page rendering** after build steps

### **Testing Requirements**

- **Page rendering**: Verify all pages display correctly after build
- **Navigation functionality**: Test all navigation buttons and links
- **Cross-browser compatibility**: Ensure consistent behavior
- **Responsive design**: Test navigation on different screen sizes

